# teaser: Create the perfect Instagram Caption
- id: 1201-instagram-caption
  title: Instagram Caption
  tags:
  - writing
  - instagram
  - caption
  family: writing
  body: 'We are a study abroad agency based in Nigeria, Our main goal on social media
    is get student that are interested in studying abroad. I want you to help me write
    an instagram caption. the caption MUST follow the following rules. RULE 1: the
    caption should be relevant to the topic RULE 2: the caption should not exceed
    instagram caption character limit RULE 3: you should include emojis to make it
    more appealing RULE 4: Include at least 25 relevant hashtags the topic for the
    caption is [PROMPT] all the output should be in [TARGETLANGUAGE]'
  enabled: true
  required:
  - prompt
  - targetlanguage
